data.description: Welcome home to this stunning Craftsman-style residence in the sought-after Woodbridge Crossing subdivision! Boasting solid construction and a wealth of features, this 4-bedroom, 3.5 -bathroom gem is the epitome of comfortable and stylish living. Step inside to discover the inviting open floor plan, adorned with upgraded hardwoods throughout the main level. The heart of the home is the well-appointed kitchen, complete with rich cabinetry, a convenient island, granite countertops, upgraded backsplash, and stainless steel appliances. The designer kitchen seamlessly flows into the spacious great room, featuring an elegant fireplace and carefully curated lighting. An additional bright and airy room off the kitchen provides versatile space for a larger dining area, or a cozy kids' playroom. Double glass doors effortlessly connect the main living room to the expansive deck, perfect for outdoor entertaining offering additional natural lighting. Upstairs, the generously sized master suite awaits, offering an oversized sitting room, dual closets with custom built-ins, a trey ceiling, and a master bath that exudes luxury. The master bath features two vanities with upgraded framed mirrors, a large shower, and a separate tub, creating a spa-like retreat. The secondary bedrooms are equally spacious, adorned with neutral paint and plush carpeting. Conveniently located upstairs is the laundry room, ensuring ease and efficiency in daily chores. But the true highlight of this home is the finished basement, complete with a full bath and direct access to the outside back patio. This additional space adds versatility and functionality to the property, catering to a variety of lifestyle needs. Beyond the home's impeccable interior, Woodbridge Crossing offers a delightful gated community experience with amenities such as a covered bridge overlooking a babbling creek, a kids' playground, and a saltwater pool with a clubhouse. Tucked away yet conveniently close to the Silver Comet Trail, this location provides easy access to shopping, Smyrna Market Village, restaurants, midtown, Truist Park, and the airport. With a two-car garage, electric car charging outlet, and a location that's close to everything, this wonderful home is ready to welcome you. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours!
